Package: python3-magnetgmsh
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         python3-xmltodict (>= 0.14.2),
         python3-gmsh (>= 4.13.1),
         python3-yaml (>= 6.0),
         python3-magnetgeo (>= 0.8.0),
         python3-numpy (>= 1.24.0)
Suggests: python3-pytest
Description: Python helpers to create HiFiMagnet cads and meshes with Gmsh
 This package provides Python utilities for creating CAD models and meshes
 for high-field magnet simulations using Gmsh.
 .
 Features:
  - Load/Create CAD and Mesh with Gmsh
  - Create Gmsh mesh from Salome XAO format
  - Support for various magnet geometries (Helix, Bitter, etc.)
  - Integration with python-magnetgeo for geometry definitions

